{"tid":83461,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"5個Sneakerhead不應該犯的錯誤！","createTime":"2017-01-16T18:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T19:04:51.000Z","uid":34069,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"24cec8e52f0fcfc513f66784831eabbee866ecf2","tid":83461,"uid":34069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:01:15.000Z","msg":"第一 自大 <br />\n有的sneakerhead買了超限量的球鞋之後就開始看不起別人！<br />\n<br />\n第二 沒有預算<br />\n還有的sneakerhead就是在有經濟壓力情況下盲目追求熱門鞋款<br />\n<br />\n第三 把錢都花在鞋子上 <br />\n還有的sneakerhead就是只顧著買鞋子，卻沒有很好的衣服褲去搭配！<br />\n<br />\n第四 便宜沒好貨 <br />\n我們總認為便宜就沒有好貨，其實這些限量鞋款貴是因為貨量少被炒起來的價格，鞋子本身材質和普通鞋款是沒有區別的！<br />\n<br />\n第五 衝動<br />\n常常看到有人到鞋店買了鞋子後又不穿直接丟床底的"},{"pid":"57d615294ac11d96a8a6a7938a5525c7111ca954","tid":83461,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:02:26.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"1d2aa29ceeb859413811ea58fc05dab696740c03","tid":83461,"uid":58,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:14:24.000Z","msg":"3其實都真，見人鳩襯啲yeezy真係無眼睇"},{"pid":"97331909b987da41b0cb8203603a2190776b5730","tid":83461,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:19:08.000Z","msg":"抄小屁鞋？<br />\n連登變左content farm ?"},{"pid":"62a9f47167bc4f2ffac4b01a1e186edfc197d1f2","tid":83461,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:20:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抄小屁孩？<br />\n連登變左content farm ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8d5e80szry8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8d5e80szry8&d=KUq9LLTjIGhvWtn3ot1OSZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=5e4fa512\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8d5e80szry8</a>"},{"pid":"5cdee29fdf07794073c0c8907348601655ed49a1","tid":83461,"uid":34069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>抄小屁孩？<br />\n連登變左content farm ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8d5e80szry8\" data-